BP Plc (BP/)  Chief Executive Officer Bob
Dudley received $6.8 million in cash and shares last year, more
than three times his compensation in 2010.  The figures were released on the U.S. Securities and
Exchange Commission website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
